<HEADLINE>
FT  01 MAY 92 / Rise in unit trust investment seen
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
UNIT TRUST investments picked up in March with gross sales for the month
reaching Pounds 956.2m, the highest figure since April last year.
Sales were boosted by institutional investment ahead of last month's general
election and by private investors placing funds in personal equity plans
before the end of the tax year. Net sales for the month (gross sales minus
repurchases) were Pounds 234.9m, and the value of funds invested at the end
of the month was Pounds 56.2bn.
Lex, Page 16
