<TEXT>
Ashes to ashes. Cigar-smoking Harry Turner, the characterful chief executive
of Television South West, is moving on.
Always noted for his grand gestures, he was caught out by the grandest: his
bid of over Pounds 16m a year for his franchise. It was a touch too rich for
