reorganisation, had affected performance at Bryan Donkin, Mr Weatherby said.
Turnover in the drinks dispenser business fell significantly and the
continued improved profits at England-Worthside offset a disappointing
performance at Thermal Refrigeration. The abrasives business continued to be
affected by the recession. Action had been taken to cut costs.
